@startuml
actor User
(Login)
(Place Order)
(Checkout)

User --> (Login)
User --> (Place Order)
(Place Order) --> (Checkout)

' ── Single-line note ──────────────────────────────
note left of User : Primary end user

' ── Multi-line note ───────────────────────────────
note right of (Place Order)
	This is the core
	business use case for
	ordering products.
end note

' ── Floating note ─────────────────────────────────
note "System requires\nhigh availability" as N1

' ── Note with color ───────────────────────────────
note right of (Login) #LightYellow
	Must support SSO
	and MFA
end note

' ── Note on link ──────────────────────────────────
(Place Order) --> (Checkout) : proceeds to
note on link : Must validate cart first

@enduml
